Biogeography of 
<taxonomicName id="FBD74D2E721836632921FD0A5922C3E8" box="[364,527,697,723]" class="Arachnida" family="Fortuyniidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Sarcoptiformes" pageId="31" pageNumber="32" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Fortuyniidae</taxonomicName>
